---
import logo from '../assets/Logo InaEEWS_New-23.png';
---

<footer class="w-full bg-black border-t border-slate-800 pt-16 pb-8 px-12 md:px-24">
	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-16 md:gap-24 mb-16">
		<div class="space-y-6">
			<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
				<img src={logo.src} alt="InaEEWS" class="h-8 w-auto" />
				<span class="text-2xl font-black varela tracking-tighter text-white">InaEEWS</span>
			</div>
			<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium">
				Indonesia Earthquake Early Warning System — Sistem peringatan dini gempa bumi untuk melindungi masyarakat Indonesia.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="space-y-6">
			<h4 class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-400">Media Sosial</h4>
